  <md:title>How Economists Use Theories and Models to Understand Economic Issues</md:title>
  <md:abstract><para id="para-00001">By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para>
<list id="list-00001">
<item>Interpret a circular flow diagram</item>
<item>Explain the importance of economic theories and models</item>
<item>Describe goods and services markets and labor markets</item>
