<problem id="fs-idp66222912">
<para id="fs-idp70743888">Suppose, as an economist, you are asked to analyze an issue unlike anything you have ever done before. Also, suppose you do not have a specific model for analyzing that issue. What should you do? <emphasis effect="italics">Hint: </emphasis> What would a carpenter do in a similar situation? </para>
    </problem>
